-- Hastoe Capital Said to Sell 100 Million Pounds of 30-Year Bonds
-- B y   K a t i e   L i n s e l l
-- 2012-03-20T09:12:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-20/hastoe-capital-said-to-sell-100-million-pounds-of-30-year-bonds.html
Hastoe Capital Plc plans to sell
100 million pounds of 30-year bonds that may be priced to yield
215 to 225 basis points more than U.K. government debt,
according to a banker involved in the transaction. RBC Capital
Markets and  Banco Santander SA (SAN)  are managing the sale.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Katie Linsell in London at 
 klinsell@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
